  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-07-13",
    "date": "2022-12-09T20:27:08Z",
    "text": "Public Health Air Quality Act of 2022\n\nThis bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to take specified actions related to monitoring and improving air quality, including by implementing a program to administer or conduct emissions measurement and quantification, promulgating regulations related to specified source categories, and deploying not fewer than 1,000 air quality sensors."
